name: Limo St. Louis
description: Limo St. Louis, a family owned St. Louis
overview: Limo St. Louis, a family owned St. Louis based Limousine Company, specializes in leasing new, Sprinter Limousines, manufactured by Mercedes Benz. All of the limousines are brand new, and have less then 5,000 miles. From the plush leather, wood trim, multiple flat screen T.V. w/ satellite, wet bar with fridge, and a suburb audio system, Sprinter Limos are extremely spacious and are perfect for weddings, family events, winery trips, dinner parties, holidays, vacations, or just a fun night out on the town with friends.
